$SectionBody1 = qq~<p>YaBB is one of the world's leading providers of free, Perl-based message board systems for webmasters. Our innovative system allows people to get and stay connected in an easy to use, easy to understand format. Come see what hundreds of thousands of webmasters and millions of registered users already know!</p>
<p><!--For additional help, please visit <a href="http://www.yabbforum.com/codex/" target="_blank"><b>The YaBB Codex</b></a>.-->
