<p>Since the last release of YaBB, <i>many new features have been introduced</i>, so take your time reading through these <b>Help</b> files.</p>
<p>You may use the menu on the left to quickly jump to any topic below.</p>
<p>You may use this <img src="{top_img}" alt="Back to Top" title="Back to Top" /> button at the bottom right of each Help section to return to the top of the Help page</p>
